    {
      "kind": "content",
      "content": [
        {
          "anchor": "overview",
          "level": 2,
          "text": "Overview",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "The composition tracks the Core Animation layer time and is rendered directly at the current dimensions of the "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": false,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/quartz/qccompositionlayer"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " object."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "An archived "
            },
            {
              "type": "codeVoice",
              "code": "QCCompositionLayer"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " object saves the composition thatâ€™s loaded at the time the layer is archived. It detects layer usage and pauses or resumes the composition appropriately. A "
            },
            {
              "type": "codeVoice",
              "code": "QCCompositionLayer"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " object starts rendering the composition automatically when the layer is placed in a visible layer hierarchy. The layer stops rendering when it is hidden or removed from the visible layer hierarchy."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "You can pass data to the input ports, or retrieve data from the output ports, of the root patch of a composition by accessing the "
            },
            {
              "type": "codeVoice",
              "code": "patch"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " attribute of the "
            },
            {
              "type": "codeVoice",
              "code": "QCCompositionLayer"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " instance using methods provided by the "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/quartz/qccompositionrenderer"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " protocol. "
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "aside",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "inlineContent": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "You must not modify the "
                },
                {
                  "type": "codeVoice",
                  "code": "asynchronous"
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": " property of the superclass "
                },
                {
                  "type": "reference",
                  "isActive": true,
                  "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/quartzcore/caopengllayer"
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "."
                }
              ]
            }
          ],
